<h2 class="bold font-l">Raiden Sends a Message Back</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The worst outcome has happened Shao Kahn has won, he has absorbed the power of Blaze and Raiden is moments from death. To save everything Raiden sends a message back in time to prevent this future from ever happening. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SetRightWhatOnceWentWrong" class='trope-example-link'>Set Right What Once Went Wrong</a></p>
</div>
